    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms are slightly browned, reduce the heat to low and break them up with a wooden spoon</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a small knob of<strong> butter alternative</strong> with the <strong>sliced shallot </strong>and <strong>chopped garlic</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>garam masala</strong>, <strong>curry powder </strong>and <strong>ginger paste </strong>and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
