    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>white long grain rice</strong> and 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[525ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>with your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and <strong>sultanas</strong></p>",
